{"thi-ap31:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap31:0.2":"Khattiyavagga ","thi-ap31:0.3":"1 Yasavatipamukhaattharasabhikkhunisahassaapadana ","thi-ap31:1.1":"“Bhava sabbe parikkhina, ","thi-ap31:1.2":"bhava santi vimocita; ","thi-ap31:1.3":"Sabbasava ca no natthi, ","thi-ap31:1.4":"arocema mahamune. ","thi-ap31:2.1":"Purimam kusalam kammam, ","thi-ap31:2.2":"yam kinci sadhupatthitam; ","thi-ap31:2.3":"Paribhogamayam dinnam, ","thi-ap31:2.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamune. ","thi-ap31:3.1":"Buddhapaccekabuddhanam, ","thi-ap31:3.2":"savakananca patthitam; ","thi-ap31:3.3":"Paribhogamayam dinnam, ","thi-ap31:3.4":"tuyhatthaya mahamune. ","thi-ap31:4.1":"Uccanicamayam kammam, ","thi-ap31:4.2":"bhikkhunam sadhupatthitam; ","thi-ap31:4.3":"Uccakulaparikammam, ","thi-ap31:4.4":"katametam mahamune. ","thi-ap31:5.1":"Teneva sukkamulena, ","thi-ap31:5.2":"codita kammasampada; ","thi-ap31:5.3":"Manusikamatikkanta, ","thi-ap31:5.4":"jayimsu khattiye kule. ","thi-ap31:6.1":"Uppatte ca kate kamme, ","thi-ap31:6.2":"jatiya vapi ekato; ","thi-ap31:6.3":"Pacchime ekato jata, ","thi-ap31:6.4":"khattiya kulasambhava. ","thi-ap31:7.1":"Rupavati bhogavati, ","thi-ap31:7.2":"labhasakkarapujita; ","thi-ap31:7.3":"Antepure mahavira, ","thi-ap31:7.4":"devanam viya nandane. ","thi-ap31:8.1":"Nibbinditva agaramha, ","thi-ap31:8.2":"pabbajimhanagariyam; ","thi-ap31:8.3":"Katipaham upadaya, ","thi-ap31:8.4":"sabba pattamha nibbutim. ","thi-ap31:9.1":"Civaram pindapatanca, ","thi-ap31:9.2":"paccayam sayanasanam; ","thi-ap31:9.3":"Upanenti bahu amhe, ","thi-ap31:9.4":"sada sakkatapujita. ","thi-ap31:10.1":"Kilesa jhapita amham, ","thi-ap31:10.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","thi-ap31:10.3":"Nagiva bandhanam chetva, ","thi-ap31:10.4":"viharama anasava. ","thi-ap31:11.1":"Svagatam vata no asi, ","thi-ap31:11.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","thi-ap31:11.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thi-ap31:11.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap31:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap31:12.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","thi-ap31:12.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","thi-ap31:12.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap31:13.1":"Ittham sudam yasavatipamukhani khattiyakannabhikkhuniyo attharasasahassani bhagavato sammukha ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap31:14.1":"Yasavatipamukhaattharasabhikkhunisahassapadanam pathamam. "}